Title:
CIPS_Initial Measurement Model 3 (mm3); without the indicators of probsolv &
persistance & with a combined variable CombSiSp(sightwrd & spell)
DATA:
FILE IS C:\Users\Oxana\Documents\CIPS2.csv;
VARIABLE:
NAMES ARE idorig CombSiSp YearProg ParentIn PALS alphknow sightwrd spell
numbers geometry measures selfcont cooperat social initiat persist probsolv
PIcat InToNeed gender AdultFam FamSize ethnicit caregiv educatPC ChildFam;
USEVARIABLES ARE CombSiSp YearProg ParentIn PALS alphknow numbers 
geometry measures selfcont cooperat social initiat;
CATEGORICAL ARE YearProg ParentIn;
MISSING ARE ALL (-99);
Analysis:
STARTS = 20;
MODEL:
! Measurement model (CFAs)
Math by numbers geometry measures;
Literacy by PALS alphknow CombSiSp;
SocSkill by selfcont cooperat social initiat;
! No Error covariances
! Structural model where all factors (and stand alone variables not intended 
! as indicators) are allowed to covary freely with each other.
ParentIn with YearProg Math Literacy SocSkill;
YearProg with Math Literacy SocSkill;
Math with Literacy SocSkill;
Literacy with SocSkill;
OUTPUT: SAMPSTAT STDYX MODINDICES (3.841);